he didn't burn this whole place down.

261
00:12:14.776 --> 00:12:15.776
[Delilah] Mm.

262
00:12:16.528 --> 00:12:18.088
-Make sure you check...
-[Charlie] Okay.

263
00:12:18.905 --> 00:12:20.866
-[sighs]
