so... I feel lucky.

341
00:15:49.366 --> 00:15:51.368
Well. I mean. it... it's not luck.

342
00:15:51.451 --> 00:15:53.912
I mean. I know how hard you work.

343
00:15:53.995 --> 00:15:56.539
Or I knew.

344
