364
00:17:01.563 --> 00:17:04.273
Okay. and now who's the freak. Dr. Florek?

365
00:17:04.357 --> 00:17:05.525
I'm okay with that.

366
00:17:05.608 --> 00:17:07.819
Two total freaks.

367
00:17:07.902 --> 00:17:11.698
You'll be a famous writer
and I'll be a world-class doctor.

368
